---
title: Chicken Breast Chow Mein with Peppers and Green Beans
description: Recreate this classic Chinese noodle dish in less time than it takes for you to decide what you want for dinner. Containing two of your five-a-day, requiring minimal washing up, and on the table in 20 minutes, for a quick-fix dinner that delivers on taste and time, this recipe is about to shoot to the top of your recipe leader board. We’ll send your compliments to the chef!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-breast-chow-mein-81d0189d-446a7561.jpg
